    <tier id="COLLOQ_ROG-dialog-0039" speaker="ROG-dialog-0039" category="colloq" type="a" display-name="ROG-dialog-0039 [colloq]">
      <event start="T1-067" end="T3-663">Se spomneš, k@šno je blo vreme še pred cajti? </event>
      <event start="T3-663" end="T4-3">Tko. </event>
      <event start="T23-119" end="T23-906">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T23-906" end="T26-397">sej še prejš@n teden blo tko ... zlo toplo. </event>
      <event start="T26-397" end="T27-771">In zdej kr ohladitev. </event>
      <event start="T42-893" end="T45-778">Vsako leto neki ... novi rekordi. </event>
      <event start="T45-778" end="T47-179">Neke nove temperature ... </event>
      <event start="T54-41" end="T55-925">Aaa. </event>
      <event start="T55-925" end="T57-656">Kaj bi mogli ukrepat? </event>
      <event start="T64-483" end="T66-321">A da b se vsi vozili z avtobusi? </event>
      <event start="T72-786" end="T74-04">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T74-04" end="T76-819">Kolko hre za delat te baterije? </event>
      <event start="T86-734" end="T88-486">A drugi teden pa spet dež? </event>
      <event start="T108-856" end="T109-733">Prov burja. </event>
      <event start="T116-909" end="T118-013">Sneh? </event>
      <event start="T118-675" end="T119-39">Teha pa že dolh. </event>
      <event start="T124-325" end="T126-021">Tle, če ne hreš pod hribe ... </event>
      <event start="T132-189" end="T43">In na Lokvi je zmeri manj, </event>
      <event start="T43" end="T134-09">se mi zdi. </event>
      <event start="T142-088" end="T49">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T49" end="T143-754">lani se spomnim ... [zvok] </event>
      <event start="T143-754" end="T145-588">Smo bli hor vsaki teden. </event>
      <event start="T156-994" end="T158-868">Ma ja, zej ... </event>
      <event start="T169-454" end="T56">Ma ja, </event>
      <event start="T56" end="T171-905">zdej sm se že navadu, k je blo toplo. </event>
      <event start="T171-905" end="T173-855">Da bo poletje zdej. </event>
      <event start="T173-855" end="T834">Ma zej ... </event>
      <event start="T834" end="T57">pravjo, da bo spet dež, </event>
      <event start="T57" end="T176-898">zej mi kr ... </event>
      <event start="T177-672" end="T178-95">In enim paše to. </event>
      <event start="T189-302" end="T64">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T64" end="T190-867">malo it ven. </event>
      <event start="T196-677" end="T198-174">In spet si samo doma. </event>
      <event start="T228-937" end="T85">Ma ja, </event>
      <event start="T85" end="T231-407">sej jaz še zmeri vsako leto natrgu. </event>
      <event start="T235-428" end="T88">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T88" end="T89">moji nonoti in ono majo še zmeri en kop drvi, </event>
      <event start="T89" end="T240-532">en kop trti. </event>
      <event start="T241-347" end="T243-481">In ... treba vsako leto pomagat. </event>
      <event start="T243-917" end="T90">So vsako leto starejši, </event>
      <event start="T90" end="T245-971">vsako leto manj. </event>
